---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Document Library
description: "Primary source materials: FOIA responses, court filings, government reports, spending records, and other evidentiary materials underlying our reporting."
permalink: /documents/
---

<div class="container">
  <div class="doc-index-layout">

    <header class="doc-index-header">
      <p class="doc-index-header__kicker">Primary Sources</p>
      <h1 class="doc-index-header__title">Document Library</h1>
      <p class="doc-index-header__body">
        Original documents underlying our reporting. FOIA responses, public records, court
        filings, government reports, and other primary sources — reproduced in full with
        context from our editors.
      </p>
    </header>

    {% if collections.documents and collections.documents.length %}
    <div class="doc-index-grid">
      {% for doc in collections.documents %}
      <article class="doc-card">
        {% if doc.data.docType %}
        <span class="doc-type-badge">{{ doc.data.docType }}</span>
        {% endif %}
        <h2 class="doc-card__title">
          <a href="{{ doc.url }}">{{ doc.data.title }}</a>
        </h2>
        {% if doc.data.description %}
        <p class="doc-card__desc">{{ doc.data.description }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="doc-card__meta">
          {% if doc.data.source %}
          <span class="doc-card__source">{{ doc.data.source }}</span>
          {% endif %}
          <time class="doc-card__date" datetime="{{ doc.date | htmlDateString }}">
            Added {{ doc.date | readableDate }}
          </time>
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <p style="color: var(--color-ink-muted); font-style: italic; padding: var(--space-10) 0;">
      No documents in the library yet.
    </p>
    {% endif %}

  </div>
</div>
